<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>
            Loan Repayment Calculator
        </title>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, , maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Pacifico' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
        <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.12.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
        <link rel="stylesheet", href="/static/style.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <%- include('partials/header') -%>
        <br>
        
        <div class="container emi-container">
            <div class="row well top-row" style="margin-bottom: 20px">
                <div class="col-sm col-md-6 frfc">
                    <h3><b>Loan EMI Calculator : </b></h3>
                        <form action="/emi-calculator/emi-dashboard" method="POST" class="form-group">
                            <label class="form_font"> Principal Amount :</label><br>
                            <input type="number" class="form-control" name="loan_amount" min="1" required><br>
                            <label class="form_font"> Time Period (in months) :</label><br>
                            <input type="number" class="form-control" name="period" min="1" required><br>
                            <label class="form_font"> Interest Rate :</label><br>
                            <input type="number" step="0.01" class="form-control" min="0" max="100" name="intrest_rate" required><br>
                            <input type="submit" class="btn btn-success form-control form_font" name="get_emi", value="Generate EMI">
                        </form>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm col-md-6 frsc">
                    <h3 style="text-decoration: underline"><b>Education Loan EMI Calculator : </b></h3><br>
                    <p style="font-size:16px;text-indent: 50px;text-align: justify">
                             Education Loan EMI Calculator is a smart tool that calculates your monthly EMI amount 
                             payable to the lender. Itâ€™s basically a slider where you enter the values; 
                             Principal amount (P), Time duration (N), and Rate of interest (R) to find out your EMI 
                             and figure out your finances in advance. By Clicking on Generate EMI you will get a dashboard where you can see
                             multiple options to choose.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row well">
                <div class="col">
                    <div style="padding:30px;line-height: 1.6">
                        <h3 style="text-decoration: underline"><b>Features of our Education Loan EMI Calculator : </b></h3><br>
                            <ul style="font-size:16px;">
                                <li>Candidate can see what is the EMI and Intrest Amount for different intrest rates.</li>
                                <li>Candidate can see a visual diagram which shows principle amount vs Intrest amount.</li>
                                <li>We have period table where you can see EMI and Intrest amount based on time period.</li>                        <li>We can see EMI and Intrest amount provided by bank by selecting bank in drop down.</li>
                                <li>We have clear chart of time period where you can see how EMI is distributed.</li>
                            </ul> <br>
                    
                            <p style="font-size:16px;text-indent: 50px;text-align: justify">
                                    You can request a callback and the <a href="/apply-loan"><b>Loan counsellor</b></a> will get back to you. One can check his/her <a><b>Loan eligibility</b></a>, 
                                    best intrest rates provided by bank and even apply for loans with best offers from our collabrative 
                                    banks by visiting <a><b>Foreignadmits</b></a> website.         
                            </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </body>
</html>